Description: # Ansistrip
        *Module to strip ANSI Escape codes from a string.*
        
        ## Installation
        ### Install with pip
        ```
        pip3 install -U ansistrip
        ```
        
        ## Usage
        ```
        In [1]: import ansistrip
        
        In [2]: text =  "\x1b[1m\x1b[38;5;10mtest\x1b0m"
        
        In [3]: ansistrip.ansi_strip(text)
        
        Out[3]: 'test'
        ```
        
